name: Libianca
description: '''Libianca Kenzonkinboum Fonji''' (born July 23, 2000), known mononymously as '''Libianca''', is a Cameroonian-American singer. She is best known for her breakout single "[[People (Libianca song)|People]]" (2022). She previously competed in the [[The Voice (American season 21)|21st season]] of American TV show [[The Voice (American TV series)|''The Voice'']] in 2021.
